<section id="contacto" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 border-t border-border">
  <div class="border border-border rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-16 bg-surface/40 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-accent/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="font-mono text-sm text-accent mb-3">// contacto</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        ¿Algo de tu tecnología te <span class="text-accent">quita el sueño</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mb-10">
        Cuéntamelo con tus palabras, sin tecnicismos. En 48 horas te digo si puedo ayudarte,
        cómo lo haría y cuánto costaría. Sin compromiso.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="mailto:contactoprofesional.designing636@passmail.net"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-md bg-accent text-bg font-medium hover:bg-accent/90 transition"
        >
          Contacto
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sergioherrerocruz"
          target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-accent/50 transition font-medium"
        >
          LinkedIn →
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sermanes"
          target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-accent/50 transition font-medium"
        >
          GitHub →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 text-sm text-muted font-mono flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-4 border-t border-border">
  <div>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Sergio Herrero — built with Astro</div>
  <div class="text-accent/70">$ uptime: 100%</div>
</footer>
